name: Jungle Raid
overview: Published in Radio Elettronica & Computer 1988/10 and as part of Bogies Pick Value Pack 5. Dropped behind enemy lines George Chesthair must battle against the baddies and in the long cherished style of old...shoot the hell out of anything that moves! You need fast reactions, digital dexterity and all the other cliched things they always write about in scenarios like this. Good luck! I think at this point I'm supposed to say in a deep and meaningful style....YOU'LL NEED IT.
